;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">报名须知：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备报价表》（见附件）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">提供公司及相关产品资质，扫描件发邮箱。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">提供相关产品近三年三甲医院销售合同扫描件<span>2</span>份至邮箱。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有独立承担民事责任的能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有履行合同所必须具备的设备和专业知识。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family: