ont-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">工期要求：<u><span> 15 </span></u>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">服务期：<span>2</span>年</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">招标规模：预算价约<u><span> 7 </span></u>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=