\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">2.4.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">2.4.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：①投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">楼</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">805</span><span style=\"background:white\">室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2022</span><span style=\"background:\r\nwhite\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">26</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">8</span><span style=\"background:white\">时</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">30</span><span style=\"background:white\">分至</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">2022</span><span style=\"background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">5</span><span style=\"background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">18</span><span style=\"background:white\">时。联系人：刘工，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-69057406</span><span style=\"background:white\">；手机：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nbackground:white\">13626222271</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"background:white\">、</span><b>本项目采用“资格后审”，“综合评估法”</b><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-66696810</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">地址：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">联系人：沈工</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">电话：</span><span style=\"line-heigh