eight:1.5;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">0515-66696810</span><span style=\"background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">地址：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">联系人：沈工</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">电话：</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">0515-66696857</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'嫤疓B2312\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black\">地址：盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>805</span>室<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;